Introduction

Yeosang is a South Korean dancer, singer, rapper, and songwriter under KQ Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group ATEEZ, which he debuted on October 24, 2018, with the release of their first mini album "TREASURE EP.1: All to Zero".

On March 2, 2021, Yeosang made his first appearance as an MC for SBS MTV's The Show. Despite initially leaving his position on December 14, 2021, it was revealed on January 18, 2022 that Yeosang would be coming back. On March 5, 2024, it was announced that he would be stepping down of his MC position.
